{"id":"guide/i18n-common-overview","title":"常见的国际化任务","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"common-internationalization-tasks\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a67g6jmq6or5i8ay6ee03uibj\">常见的国际化任务<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#common-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8nqp8o4eenql6ou498zd9y9ic\">使用以下 Angular 任务来国际化你的项目。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dpxnj32v9fb2sh821dt8aitmz\">使用内置管道以本地格式显示日期、数字、百分比和货币。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4pa2yzunvhh1c3wwri54lcf86\">在组件模板中标记文本以进行翻译。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7mn4exaf658a1vtibykjceosi\">标记复数形式的表达式以供翻译。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1xvcu5wpffpyx70k3toiyy36o\">标记替代文本以进行翻译。</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"acuj103cgcpuod032e5ofzend\">在为国际受众准备好项目之后，可以使用 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 来本地化你的项目。完成以下任务以本地化你的项目。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2jfykplg9m1aw5qaxvprjigh3\">使用 CLI 将标记的文本提取到<em>源语言</em>文件中。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9e1vu0lbowlq34uk0rddwqffw\">为每种语言制作一份<em>源语言</em>文件的副本，并将所有<em>翻译</em>文件发送给翻译人员或翻译服务。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7i4plkwiv4w398p4gcsm11rtm\">在为一种或多种语言环境构建项目时，使用 CLI 合并已完成的翻译文件。</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"64avgvpxk5t4a789x2zj4fptj\">为所有目标语言环境创建一个强适应性的用户界面，将不同语言的间距等差异考虑在内。有关更多详细信息，请参阅<a href=\"https://marketfinder.thinkwithgoogle.com/intl/en_us/guide/how-to-approach-i18n#overview\" title=\"Overview - How to approach internationalization | Market Finder | Think with Google\">如何进行国际化</a>。</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e44b21uig1fakj5vcfuvz1bdu\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2vwgfyttxbb5i4tqwwfwv9zea\">要准备翻译项目，你应该对以下主题有基本的了解。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"52nvnkmh4saprg8vamomnwca1\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">模板</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"vaetn8gsmwrpj42ci4hqh18y\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">组件</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1r1jmjyx0gbtudese178lmo75\"><a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> <a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">命令行</a>，管理 Angular 开发周期的工具</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"db650j48xko27f6o1xuqp3v8h\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> 用于翻译文件</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2uwjh4tfqejo04e9rjzgv0b8o\">了解常见的 Angular 国际化任务<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Add the localize package\">\n        <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4byiubykxo4pfqxbc605ynmub\">添加 localize 包</section>\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bw5fgohu5kgwbhk3sx6s4lzp\">学习如何往项目中添加 Angular 的 localize 包</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4byiubykxo4pfqxbc605ynmub\">添加 localize 包</p>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID\">\n        <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bc6xme8exwc8bvmac4dwvol68\">通过 ID 引用语言环境</section>\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"rxpg77c4i47qapfdgjgqub6x\">学习如何标识语言环境标识符，并将其添加到项目</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bc6xme8exwc8bvmac4dwvol68\">通过 ID 引用语言环境</p>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Format data based on locale\">\n        <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"23u4rd5ufxutyammmlq8zso15\">基于语言环境格式化数据</section>\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"28thr2kkihaoj2gq416umvksb\">学习如何实现本地化数据管道，以及为项目改写默认语言环境</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"23u4rd5ufxutyammmlq8zso15\">基于语言环境格式化数据</p>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Prepare component for translation\">\n        <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2bj8f466inlapqxogmicf5uhy\">准备翻译组件</section>\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b3fqrlujdf0faltzkvt94rf21\">学习如何指定要翻译的源文本</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2bj8f466inlapqxogmicf5uhy\">准备翻译组件</p>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-translation-files\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Work with translation files\">\n        <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"984sg0n2lojjl66czjjoq9x3v\">使用翻译文件</section>\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5wyn1yn3u9a3h4s1dtuwmktd1\">学习如何检查和处理翻译文件</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"984sg0n2lojjl66czjjoq9x3v\">使用翻译文件</p>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-merge\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Merge translations into the application\">\n        <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1nwoy17z6x4hhc1h1m6fo0g5h\">把翻译结果合并回应用</section>\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"w0g5hqy7lr8v0ucmc0334nth\">学习如何合并翻译结果，并构建翻译完的应用</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1nwoy17z6x4hhc1h1m6fo0g5h\">把翻译结果合并回应用</p>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-deploy\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Deploy multiple locales\">\n        <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4f52ejc3rinwvytrc1s74trwz\">部署多个语言环境</section>\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"38e2jys7ryo6g4fh83wbj6gge\">学习如何为应用部署多个语言环境</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4f52ejc3rinwvytrc1s74trwz\">部署多个语言环境</p>\n    </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间：Thu Oct 07 2021</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\n - guide/glossary#component\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package\n - guide/i18n-common-deploy\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/i18n-common-merge\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#common-internationalization-tasks\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#prerequisites\n - guide/i18n-common-prepare\n - guide/i18n-common-translation-files\n - https://marketfinder.thinkwithgoogle.com/intl/en_us/guide/how-to-approach-i18n#overview\n - https://www.w3.org/XML\n-->"}